data.description: Santa Fe Contemporary Styling in this sanctuary of light and excellence built by the respected Joel McHorse. Sited on 2.6 acres that offers 360 views of mountain ranges and magnificent New Mexico Sky. Enter a few steps at the entry, then enjoy single level living with high ceilings, plastered great room, gallery or executive office, dining area with spacious outdoor portals and an expansive gourmet kitchen as the main features. You will love the 3,533 square feet of living space in the home, three large bedrooms and three full bathrooms. The living spaces are open and graciously flow into the outdoor patios. Modern amenities such as in-floor radiant heat, air conditioning, floor to ceiling glass, central hearth fireplace, colored concrete floors and many custom features throughout. There is an oversized, direct entry 2-car garage with a mud room for your convenience. There also is a separate, well-designed 387 square foot studio/office space. There also is over 1,000 square feet of portals and outdoor living space from which to enjoy a serene life. Private agent showings.
